column5: I'm pretty busy today but I just had to share this with you. Hope you enjoy.
you mean...one of the funniest things youve seen.....more than once...
O gawd, you and Rick both picked this thing now lol. Still great to see, shared it with everybody on Facebook.  Merry Christmas, Mike
Not to ruin it but they came from a hold to the left of the camera...you can hear the water sloshing before the older guy comes up...
Roy you having one of those giddy days where you just wanna put a smile on everyone's face for no particular reason?  Well it worked.  And thank you
Now, is it really funnier than the pic of the Catfish with the basket ball in it's mouth? By, I'd sure like to see that again! Have a great weekend Roy! HH
Man that video sure is getting around on the net Thanks Roy!!!

Yeah CPH, just another of those days here. I have 23 kidlets here today and I just checked the radar screen and  that well fed communist with the red suit and white beard  should be landing around 3:45.....gunna be long, long day.
OMG...I don't think I saw that before..that's funny!
Did you get Marc to be Santa again ?????
Are you kidding me??  It's the real Santa here. Both Marc and J are fairy Godmothers!
Well Marc Maybe...  with his chisel like figure and all..
try and find a suit to fit him-too long in the arms and legs
